Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:05.30,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s something I want to tell you, but it’s too heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.30,0:01:11.18,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this, it seems I must break
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:20.37,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many of these indescribable feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:27.21,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot deliver them to you, though you are near, the distance is great
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:36.03,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever only looking up at the blue sky is no good
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:43.26,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning around (spinning around)…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.26,0:01:50.67,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Unsteadily mustering strength, I want to try diving into your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:57.80,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning around (spinning around)…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:07.29,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightly floating, again today I am alone above the clouds
