Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:41.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong. I’m sorry, Harima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn’t bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:51.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You really changed your style.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:52.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:55.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s great, Tazawa-kun. This is much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:56.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:59.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Uh, my name is Harima.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:03.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your use of this spread is very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.58,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not “Tazawa”…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:05.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve got potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:07.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But in real life,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:13.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,things between Tenma-chan\Nand me never turn out like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:18.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I can’t let Blondie see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:21.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If Tenma-chan should ever\Nfind out what’s in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:24.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun, you’re the worst of the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:27.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl’s gonna tell her! I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:29.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she chasing me?!\NCan she be after this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you running from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:37.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t let her see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:41.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:46.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crud. Sawachika just won’t answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:50.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t even know why\Nshe came at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:53.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Harima seems to\Nbe involved in it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:54.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:00.17,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:07.81,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Café El Cado
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:10.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I dragged you in here like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:11.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. No…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:16.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can she be after my manuscript, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:19.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So the thing is… um…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:24.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask me something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:26.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So it’s about this, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You see…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:38.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:41.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it, everybody\Nfound out about my comics.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:46.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You are cute, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:48.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But why the panic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:52.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry. I see I’ve interrupted your date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:59.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there’s an important reason for this…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:05.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! To tell the truth,\NI’m drawing comics!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima! Take care of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:15.21,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx110\bord0\fnDesertDogHmk\b1\c&H31332E&\frz316.187\pos(229,319)}Iced coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:15.21,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx110\bord0\fnDesertDogHmk\b1\c&H31332E&\frz317.458\pos(294,261)}American coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:14.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But she wouldn’t, would she? Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:25.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I run from her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:32.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She really is fast. But never\Nunderestimate a martial artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder if she gave up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:18.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why’d she give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:27.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Hanai! I’m back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:31.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, I really messed up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:32.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:35.49,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I ripped my skirt, so I’m gonna\Nchange to my sparring uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell, that’s all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:40.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:41.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:47.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give Suou-san’s coat\Nand bag back to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to Suou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:55.89,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\bord1\shad1\fs40\fnAirstream\c&HF1F7FF&\3c&H010344&\pos(508,83)}KickAss
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:55.89,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy100\fsp-1\be1\shad2\3c&HFFFFFF&\fnImpact\fs72\b0\i0\c&H1A16DF&\pos(506,124)}{\fscy112}A{\fscy88}nıme
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:55.89,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1.2\be1\shad2\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs26\i1\c&HAE690B&\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\fscx65\fscy115\pos(504,139)}www.kickassanime.org
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:02.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know what’s going on, but ain’t\Nyou underestimating me a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:05.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know what’s going on, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:07.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I’d like a calm explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:08.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:11.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,since you’re a delinquent\Nwhose only answer is violence,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:15.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,sometime I wish I could teach you a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:17.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:24.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Agh! My manuscript!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:26.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not falling for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:29.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn’t he dodge it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Arm lock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:48.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You stopped, didn’t you, bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:54.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got no interest in you, and I didn’t\Nthink it was worth it to give my all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:57.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can’t stand being underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:01.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s for real now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:04.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t have to hold back, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:06.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll beat you to a pulp, head on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:20.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eri-chan? It’s me, it’s me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:25.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, about tomorrow’s fireworks show…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:28.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven’t set the place or time, yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:28.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about meeting at 5 o’clock\Nin front of the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:32.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can walk around first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:36.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:41.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, 5, then. Don’t come late, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:44.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t. I’m not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:47.49,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry! I don’t come late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:50.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it’s not 5 o’clock Tenma Time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s Tenma Time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:55.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,30 minutes over the arranged time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:58.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re mean! That’ll never, ever happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:01.72,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\fscy150\bord0\frx26\fry358\c&H31332E&\fnDesyrel\frz10.529\pos(460,215)}5 o’clock
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:01.72,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy150\fscx80\bord0\frx26\fry358\fnDesyrel\c&H31332E&\pos(479,247)\frz15.867}Meet in front of the station
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, if I’m late, I’ll treat you to ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see, about 30 cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll get fat, Eri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:10.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I’ll probably help you eat it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:11.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:14.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. ’Night, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:28.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I’m sorry.\NI don’t think I can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:41.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Sawachika’s coming…\Nto the fireworks show tomorrow night?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:44.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mail?! Sawachika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow?! It can’t be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And of all times, why now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:09.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s coming back…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, I’ll be your home tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:17.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Masahiro Kouzu. How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:21.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be so formal.\NWe’ve met before, besides.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:24.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Shall we begin, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:31.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since middle school days, Kouzu-senpai was known for his smarts,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:35.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,and our parents were friends,\Nso he came to be my home tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:38.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:40.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s… wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh… wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:45.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! I know I’m stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:50.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're correcting me so much just because\nyou don't want to teach me for free, aren't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:51.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Join our martial arts school!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:58.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Build that puny body up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we’ll be even!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:06.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,To my surprise, Kouzu-senpai really did join.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.52,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\bord0\b1\c&H030303&\fnDupree\frz32.102\frx344\fry20\pos(470,356)}Kouzu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:14.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that he was naturally smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:19.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a hard worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:22.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And, as I watched him…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,amazingly, I wanted to study harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:29.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I found that studies were\Nmore fun than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:31.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:32.79,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord0\c&H030303&\fnBritannic Bold\pos(573,424)\frx12\fry356}High\NSchool\NEntrance\NExam\NHall
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:32.88,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an5\bord0\c&H030303&\fnBritannic Bold\pos(573,424)\frx12\fry356}High\NSchool\NEntrance\NExam\NHall
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:33.04,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\an5\bord0\c&H030303&\fnBritannic Bold\pos(573,424)\frx12\fry356}High\NSchool\NEntrance\NExam\NHall
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.04,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\an5\bord0\c&H030303&\fnBritannic Bold\pos(573,424)\frx12\fry356}High\NSchool\NEntrance\NExam\NHall
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:35.04,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(329,359)}May you pass the exam\NYagami Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:58.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But once the entrance exam was over…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:03.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,… we were no longer teacher and student.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:09.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we happened to pass in the hallway,\Nwe stopped saying “hi” to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:14.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:17.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t be wasting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:20.17,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be30\p1\bord0\c&HDFA87A&\pos(97,260)}m220 162 l 403 163 413 421 229 418
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:20.17,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy125\bord0\an4\c&HA16439&\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\pos(218,214)\frz1}Subject: How are you?\N---------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:20.17,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy125\fscx90\bord0\an4\c&HA16439&\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\frz1\pos(231,337)}Hi! Kouzu-senpai is\Ncoming home, so we\Nare having a drinking\Nparty.\NThe date and time are:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This was so sudden…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:22.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:24.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:28.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But tomorrow’s the fireworks show!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:31.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What awful timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:40.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You can’t go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:44.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m really sorry! There’s just\Nsomething I can’t get out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:46.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’ll I tell Eri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:49.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m really sorry! I’ll call Sawachika.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:53.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. ’Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:59.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she’ll answer the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:06.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:08.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawachika? It’s me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:09.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:14.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um… I-It’s kind of hard to say this… I…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:21.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want to break our date,\Nno questions asked for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:22.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:24.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:27.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me honestly. Is the reason… a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:39.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Actually, the boy I like is coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:43.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I… Last year, I was too chicken\Nto tell him how I felt,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:45.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always regretted it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:47.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s been six months, and he’s coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:51.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I want to tell him this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:52.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:54.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’d choose a guy over your friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:55.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the lowest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:00.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come off it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:03.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the one who dissed me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:06.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I apologize?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:09.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m gonna settle this, here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:15.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The number you have dialed is…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:17.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! I’m going to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:26.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I’m wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:31.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a right to love, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.85,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\bord1\be1\shad1\fs40\fnAirstream\c&HF1F7FF&\3c&H010344&\pos(500,79)}Mokkori
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.85,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy100\fsp-1\be1\shad2\3c&HFFFFFF&\fnImpact\fs72\b0\i0\c&H1A16DF&\pos(503,119)}{\fscy112}F{\fscy88}ansub
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.85,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1.2\be1\shad2\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs26\i1\c&HAE690B&\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\fscy115\pos(503,134)}www.mokkori.cz
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:43.87,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\t(0,500,\c&HFFFFFF&)}Yagami Ginza
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:52.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should have had my hair done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:54.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it’s bad to seem overeager.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.75,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Netami Bar
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:58.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:02.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And it’s a bar! I’m getting\Neven more nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:06.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing. It’s just like sparring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, calm down, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll tell him… I’ll tell him everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Miko-chan! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:25.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this guy!\NHe ain’t changed one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.49,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, great to see you, Mikoto-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:29.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:32.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Masahiro, you actually\Ntutored a cutie like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:39.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shocker, ain’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:43.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This clueless, timid guy, bringing home a girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:49.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:53.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:57.97,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80\bord0\fad(200,200)\c&H01120C&\pos(449,385)\fnAggressive Angry Baby Killer}Lie
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:02.34,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80\bord0\fad(200,200)\c&H01120C&\pos(325,324)\fnAggressive Angry Baby Killer}Lie
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:59.68,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80\bord0\fad(200,200)\c&H01120C&\pos(143,420)\fnAggressive Angry Baby Killer}Please
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:16:01.94,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80\bord0\fad(200,200)\fnAggressive Angry Baby Killer\c&H01120C&\pos(547,340)}Uh
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:03.90,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80\bord0\fad(200,200)\fnAggressive Angry Baby Killer\c&H01120C&\pos(234,178)}But
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:09.87,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord0\fad(200,200)\fnAggressive Angry Baby Killer\c&H01120C&\pos(318,345)}Please
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:13.41,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80\bord0\fad(200,700)\fnAggressive Angry Baby Killer\c&H01120C&\pos(329,101)}Fool
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:15:58.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:09.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I have been…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:12.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,… a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:18.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do? The name is Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:20.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He has helped me a great deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:23.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, look at you, Teacher! She’s so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You make a great couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:28.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:33.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:37.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it. To end like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:38.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re asking me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:53.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry. I can’t go out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:55.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,’Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:00.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawachika-san was asked again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:04.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who can resist? She’s pretty\Nand gracious to everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:07.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, but don’t you think\Nshe’s getting a little too confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:10.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really. She so thinks she’s all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:13.59,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sawachika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:20.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… oh, I thought I’d take in\Na movie by myself, for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:25.23,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs18\pos(317,263)\b1\c&H170602&}Yagami Cinema
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:23.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Only horror films are playing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:25.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:28.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. I guess I’ll go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:30.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re free, come over to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:32.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re having hot pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:36.45,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs18\pos(317,263)\b1\c&H170602&}Yagami Cinema
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:36.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you gotta carry the groceries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:48.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how about having a drink with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:52.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s Miko-chan’s friend.\NReal pretty, ain’t she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:55.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it, Tetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:58.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’d never win, even if you were 20 years younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:00.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddya mean? I still got what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:03.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not go out with me and see, girlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um… I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:09.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You got shot down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:11.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:15.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Look at you, Sawachika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:18.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to party?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:21.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You forced me to come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:27.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my… You can make a face like that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:31.17,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re right. This is how I am.\NIs it a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:34.54,insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Suddenly, this endless feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:40.30,insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I feel as if it’s part of me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:46.05,insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Flowing deeply, loudly inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:51.81,insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}At times I’ve wounded and hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:55.44,insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}So let the seasons change, please stay
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:19:03.07,insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I wake up from a dream but I haven’t forgotten you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:06.36,insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Never, will I sleep again, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:14.79,insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}So, please, just let time stand still…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:17.79,insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Sweet dream forever
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:26.18,insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I love you so much, yet when I’m this close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:33.31,insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I want to be sure again, to meet you once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:37.39,insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Do you have a same feeling as me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:40.40,insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Sweet dream forever
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:46.07,insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Blindingly bright
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:32.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:35.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if people talk dirt about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:37.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,there’s no need to humble yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:39.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s tough to watch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:42.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She knows about those rumors, and yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:45.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? Don’t talk\Nas if you know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:46.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s none of…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:48.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,None of my business. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. That’s the way I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:53.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The way you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:55.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, the way I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:08.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve never seen Japanese fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let’s go to the next\Nfireworks show together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:16.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a special place for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:18.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Yagami Shrine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:23.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You go through the woods in back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:25.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a narrow and pretty rough road, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:28.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But then…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:31.49,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,if you go to the end of the road…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:48.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikoto… you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:49.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:54.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:00.17,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You see…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,0:20:02.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:08.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’d better go… for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:20.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty, aren’t they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:25.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:28.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I got dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:32.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who dumped you is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:34.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:38.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well, it was one-sided\Non my part, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:43.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was comforted by Sawachika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:47.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid, two women\Nwatching fireworks alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:53.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Tenma?\NIt’s me. I’m with Mikoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:54.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:03.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eri-chan! Miko-chan!\NI’ve brought the gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:05.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! This place has a great view!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:07.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re late, Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:09.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:10.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Sawachika.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:17.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:24.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! You won’t be\Nable to climb back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:26.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:32.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck were we fighting up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:33.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:54.33,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys are always chasing after girls
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:22:00.09,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,All day long they’re thinking of girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:04.79,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,But those boys certainly are a little stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:10.26,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,They never seem to understand girls’ feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.71,0:22:14.88,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you really really are a big dummy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:17.55,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I give you a lesson, Big Dummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.55,0:22:20.94,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the most important thing in the world is…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:23.79,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that absolutely must be…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:28.23,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s definitely “timing”, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.40,0:22:31.37,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if you wanna say “I love you”,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:34.56,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on a date, or do something…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:40.57,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, kiss, or say goodbye, at any time…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:44.58,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the most important thing in the world is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:49.49,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,definitely “timing”, I think, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:50.47,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.81,0:23:08.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our gang gets together\Non an outing for the tea club.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:11.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I see Harima talking to Yakumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.36,0:23:13.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,After Eri-chan and Miko-chan,\NHarima’s chasing Yakumo now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:15.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Her big sister won’t allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.82,0:23:17.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next on School Rumble:
